=head1 CHANGELOG

=begin item
B<v0.1.18>

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.17>

=item Take care of exceptions that throw on their own when reported
=item Fix a test that was freezing if C<$RAKUDO_MAX_THREADS> environment variable is set to a too low value

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.16>

=item Fix C<cmp-deeply> for nominalizables
=item Fix C<cmp-deeply> for paramterized hashes with non-string keys

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.15>

=item Fix C<test-assertion> trait when the assertion is used at the top level

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.14>

=item Implement C<test-assertiion> trait
=item Fix C<exit> freezing when called within a C<subtest>

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.13>

=item Fix comparing of undefined attributes

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.12>

=item Fix C<cmp-deeply> failing while reporting a C<Pair>

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.11>

=item C<isa-ok> reports types only now
=item Fix handling of TEST_JOBS environment variable

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.10>

=begin item
Make C<cmp-deeply> reports about difference in positionals or associatives more detailed by reporting different sizes
or key sets, respectively.
=end item

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.9>

=item C<diag> is now using C<**> slurpiness and gistifies its arguments, making it more C<say>-alike
=item Added C<cmp-deeply> test

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.7>

=item Make the module play well with independent threads
=item Improve warning message for tools invoked after C<done-testing>

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.6>

=item Fixed a critical bug in slang which was breaking role declarations

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.5>

=item Fixed compatibility with Rakudo compiler new-disp implementation

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.4>

=item Mostly bug fix release
=item Added C<:timeout> parameter to C<is-run>

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.3>

=item Improved handling of exceptions
=item Subtests now attempt to report any exception produced by their body rather than bailing out immediately
=item New method on Aggregator role: event-queue-active
=item A couple of minor fixes

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.2>

=item Fixed a rare bug causing C<throws-like> to throw itself.

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.1>

=item Fixed a tool call stack race condition
=item Fixed a todo+subtest race condition and extra todo count consumption

=end item

=begin item
B<v0.1.0>

=item Implemented tool call stack and tool anchoring
(L<C<Test::Async::Manual>|rakudoc:Test::Async::Manual>)
=item Added support for pre-comments, or header comments, to
L<C<Test::Async::Event::Test>|rakudoc:Test::Async::Event::Test>
=item Added a header to the output of non-hiddent subtests, similar to
L<a Rakudo request ticket|https://github.com/rakudo/rakudo/issues/4266>
=item Implemented auto-registration for inline C<test-bundle> declarations
=item Added C<abort-testing> tool
=end item

